                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6589" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0190</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9894 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">图于未萌，虑于未有——大数据背景下步步高供应链风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Batten Down the Hatches: Supply Chain Risk Management of BBG Company under the Background of Big Data</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周兰，何浩源，陈国庆，秦旭，朱胤鸣，汪阳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">步步高商业连锁股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理；供应链管理；大数据；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Risk management; Supply chain management; Big data</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“十四五”提出了要大力发展数字经济，数字经济能够通过大数据、人工智能、区块链等技术驱动供应链协同创新赋能，不断增强供应链的敏捷性、适应性和协调性。零售企业处于供应链末端，直面复杂多变的市场环境，是推动供应链数宇化，提升供应链抗风险能力的“排头兵”。本文以中国企业五百强步步高公司为案例主体，阐述了步步高公司对供应链风险管理的优化。在对供应链各环节风险识别和评估之后，步步高发现供应链风险的根源就在于各环节存在的“信息孤岛”，并由此构建了“一核两翼，五环相链”的大数据应对方案。该方案以主数据管理共享中心为核心，以双循环信息共享平台中的内部信息循环和外部信息循环为两大侧翼，串联五大供应链业务环节。通过实施该方案，步步高有效地应对了供应链风险，实现了差异化和具有竞争力的供应链管理目标，对同行业其他企业极具借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The &quot;14th Five-Year Plan&quot; proposes to vigorously develop the digital economy. The digital economy can drive the collaborative innovation and empowerment of the supply chain through technologies such as big data, artificial intelligence, and blockchain, and continuously enhance the agility, adaptability and coordination of the supply chain. Retail companies are at the end of the supply chain, facing the complex and changing market environment, and they are the &quot;pioneers&quot; to promote the digitalization of the supply chain and improve the supply chain&#39;s ability to resist risks. This paper takes BBG Company, one of the top 500 Chinese enterprises, as the main case, and expounds the optimization of BBG Company&#39;s supply chain risk management. After identifying and evaluating the risks in each link of the supply chain, BBG found that the root cause of the supply chain risk is the most common &quot;information island&quot; in each link, and thus built a &quot;one core, two wings, five links and links&quot; big data coping plan. The plan takes the master data management and sharing center as the core, takes the internal information cycle and external information cycle in the dual-cycle information sharing platform as the two flanks, and connects five supply chain business links. By implementing this plan, BBG has effectively responded to supply chain risks and achieved differentiated and competitive supply chain management goals, which is of great reference to other companies in the same industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制专题》、《大数据与风险管理》、《供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链管理；风险管理；PEST分析；战略地图；供应链管理；大数据</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
